  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Then to-- to clean the streets, then to bring things from one side of the town to the other side of the town, to schlep things from one street to another, just to make the people suffer-- so these were the first signs of-- of a very special approach to Jews.",
      "word_count": 55
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We did-- yeah?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the beginning, yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I-- as far as I remember, it took about four months that they let the Jewish students-- they allowed them to-- to go on in studying.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "After, I think, four months-- I think until the-- the end of '39, maybe the beginning of '40, they stopped and closed-- first of all, closed the-- the Jewish schools.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And one of the worst-- first ones which was rolled closed was the Hebrew school.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then they expelled every Jew-- Jewish student from-- from the Polish school, because many, many of the Jewish kids were going to-- to public schools.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The Hebrew school was a private school.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So they expelled all the children, and that was [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "This was the time of-- of general education of Jews in Poland, as far as I know.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This began, also-- this began, also, quite quickly.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't remember exactly the-- the dates.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But it was-- the policy of Germans was the bigger the business was, too put a so-called-- they-- they called it, in German, [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That means a man, whom they trust, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] over the-- upon the-- the-- the owner or the manager of-- of the business.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And this man was-- in the beginning, he had to control the business, and to take all the money, and to control it.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
